Afrobeat music star Seun Anikulapo Kuti has weighed in on the raging discussion over Oxlade’s nude picture and sex tape. The son of the famous Afrobeat pioneer, Fela Kuti, took to his Instagram account to caution fans and followers from sharing the singer’s nude pictures and sex tape.   They don’t want me to see my children, Blackface cries out     Actor Yomi Fabiyi welcomes baby boy     Mercy Aigbe promises to be mother-of-the-day for fans   “Stop flooding my timeline with someone else’s sex stories abeg. Y’ all are infants. Grow up and face serious ish!! Jerez,” Kuti wrote. Continuing, he said: “For a country that is over 90 per cent religious. You and your kids are really fascinated by sex. father and mother’s uncle and aunty, brothers and sister. I sure say una deh look porn inside church and mosque sef.”